---
// ProblemsSection コンポーネント - Modern Design
---

<section id="problems" class="section-padding bg-muted/30">
  <div class="container-custom">
    <div class="text-center mb-20">
      <h2 class="mb-6">
        研究者が直面する<span class="text-gradient">現実的な課題</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-muted-foreground max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        多くの研究者が抱える共通の悩みを解決します
      </p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <div class="card-modern p-8 group hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300">
        <div class="text-5xl mb-6 filter grayscale group-hover:grayscale-0 transition-all duration-300">😰</div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4 group-hover:text-primary transition-colors">外国人参加者集めの困難</h3>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">言語の壁、文化の違い、信頼関係構築の難しさ</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="card-modern p-8 group hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300">
        <div class="text-5xl mb-6 filter grayscale group-hover:grayscale-0 transition-all duration-300">⏰</div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4 group-hover:text-secondary transition-colors">時間とコストの負担</h3>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">研究本来の業務以外の事務作業に時間を取られる</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="card-modern p-8 group hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300">
        <div class="text-5xl mb-6 filter grayscale group-hover:grayscale-0 transition-all duration-300">📄</div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4 group-hover:text-gradient transition-colors">書類翻訳の負担</h3>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">専門的な研究文書の正確な翻訳が必要</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>